## Screen Inventory

| Screen Name | Purpose | Primary User |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Dashboard | View mission statistics and pending actions | All Users |
| Mission List | View and search all missions | Assigned Person |
| Create Mission | Create a new mission request | Assigned Person |
| Mission Details | View mission information and workflow progress | All Users |
| Pending Approvals | Approve or reject mission requests | Line Manager, Division Manager |
| Travel Cost Review | Enter and review travel-related costs | Travel Team |
| Payments | Review approved amounts and confirm payment | Treasury |
| Mission Extensions | Request and manage mission extensions | Assigned Person |
| Mission Closure | Close mission and upload supporting documents | Assigned Person |
| Settlements | Calculate and process mission settlement | Finance |
| Employee Mission History Report | View mission history by employee | Finance |
| Debit / Credit Report | View employee balances and settlement results | Finance |